msgstr "Creating Custom Modules"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:10
msgid "继承 EnvBase"
msgstr "Inherit from EnvBase"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:12
msgid "要创建自定义环境模块，请继承 ``EnvBase`` 并实现必需的方法："
msgstr "To create a custom environment module, inherit from ``EnvBase`` and implement the required methods:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:15
msgid "需要实现的方法"
msgstr "Required Methods to Implement"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:17
msgid "创建自定义环境模块时，必须实现："
msgstr "When creating a custom environment module, you must implement:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:19
msgid "**def observe(self) -> str**"
msgstr "**def observe(self) -> str**"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:21
msgid "返回模块当前状态的字符串描述。 这用于为智能体生成世界描述。"
msgstr "Return a string description of the current state of the module. This is used to generate the world description for agents."

#: ../../env_modules.rst:24
msgid "返回:"
msgstr "Returns:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:25
msgid "描述模块当前状态的字符串"
msgstr "A string describing the module's current state"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:27
msgid "**async def step(self, tick: int, t: datetime) -> None**"
msgstr "**async def step(self, tick: int, t: datetime) -> None**"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:29
msgid "执行一个模拟步骤。在 AgentSociety 模拟期间自动调用。 使用此方法更新时间相关的状态。"
msgstr "Execute one simulation step. This is called automatically during AgentSociety simulations. Use this to update time-dependent state."

#: ../../env_modules.rst:32
msgid "参数:"
msgstr "Parameters:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:33
msgid "tick: 此步骤的持续时间（秒） t: 此步骤后的当前模拟日期时间"
msgstr "tick: Duration of this step in seconds t: Current simulation datetime after this step"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:36
msgid "**使用 @tool 装饰的工具**"
msgstr "**Tools decorated with @tool**"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:38
msgid "使用 ``@tool`` 装饰器将方法公开为智能体的可调用函数。"
msgstr "Use the ``@tool`` decorator to expose methods as callable functions for agents."

