msgstr "``PrisonersDilemma`` - Prisoner's dilemma module"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:74
msgid "@tool 装饰器"
msgstr "The @tool Decorator"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:76
msgid "``@tool`` 装饰器将方法标记为可被智能体调用："
msgstr "The ``@tool`` decorator marks methods as callable by agents:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:87
msgid "参数："
msgstr "Parameters:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:89
msgid "**readonly** (bool): 工具是否修改环境 * ``True`` = 只读，可用于查询 * ``False`` = 修改状态，可用于干预"
msgstr "**readonly** (bool): Whether the tool modifies the environment * ``True`` = read-only, can be used in queries * ``False`` = modifies state, can be used in interventions"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:93
msgid "**kind** (str): 工具的类型 * ``\"observe\"``: 单参数观察（需要 readonly=True） * ``\"statistics\"``: 聚合查询（无参数，需要 readonly=True） * ``None`` 或省略: 常规工具（任何签名，任何 readonly 值）"
msgstr "**kind** (str): The type of tool * ``\"observe\"``: Single-parameter observations (requires readonly=True) * ``\"statistics\"``: Aggregate queries (no parameters, requires readonly=True) * ``None`` or omitted: Regular tool (any signature, any readonly value)"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:99
msgid "工具类型"
msgstr "Tool Types"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:101
msgid "**observe**: 单参数观察（需要 readonly=True）"
msgstr "**observe**: Single-parameter observations (readonly=True required)"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:102
msgid "**statistics**: 聚合查询（无参数，需要 readonly=True）"
msgstr "**statistics**: Aggregate queries (no parameters, readonly=True required)"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:103
msgid "**regular**: 任何其他工具（可以是只读或读写）"
msgstr "**regular**: Any other tool (can be readonly or read-write)"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:105
msgid "有关工具类型的更多详情，请参阅 :doc:`concepts`。"
msgstr "See :doc:`concepts` for more details on tool types."

